# Drop exported Grafana dashboard JSON files in this directory.
# See docs/runbooks/grafana-dashboards-export.md for the procedure.
#
# Files dropped here are bind-mounted into the Grafana container
# at /var/lib/grafana/dashboards/ and auto-imported by the
# bezaforge provisioning provider (see ../provisioning/dashboards/bezaforge.yaml).
#
# Subdirectories are honored — Grafana renders the folder
# structure (foldersFromFilesStructure: true). Example layout:
#   dashboards/Infrastructure/host-overview.json
#   dashboards/Services/jellyfin.json
#   dashboards/Logs/loki-explore.json
